                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-60-off341 t17910413-60-cd342"></join>, a piece of printed callico, containing twenty-eight yards, value 20 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910413-60-victim695" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Clay
                  <interp inst="t17910413-60-victim695" type="surname" value="Clay"></interp>
